Changelog:

Version 1.1 (2017-01-13)
* suppress version mismatch errors when testing
  multiple protocols

Version 1.0 (2016-01-11)
* make sure we push to arrays

Version 0.9 (2016-12-19)
* don't unset previous weight value
* additional debugging output

Version 0.8 (2016-12-15)
* add '-D' to allow sleeping in between openssl(1) invocations

Version 0.7 (2016-12-12)
* allow hostname:port to be given
* add '-S' to allow SNI
* detect server reset, but move on

Version 0.6 (2016-11-30)
* add '-l' to list ciphers one per line
* add '-t' to list ciphers by protocol
* use '-servername' so SNI works as expected

Version 0.5 (2016-11-29)
* support services which only offer a single cipher
* abort on connection timeouts

Version 0.4 (2016-11-08)
* test absolutely all ciphers

Version 0.3 (2016-11-07)
* add '-V' to display version information
* clarify and update exit codes
* don't print anything if no differences are found
* catch older openssl(1) handshake error messages

Version 0.2 (2016-11-03)
* add '-d' option to display unified diff(1) output

Version 0.1 (2016-10-31)
* initial version - boo!
